<p>但是用 <strong>Android Studio</strong> 的 <strong>New Flutter project</strong> 时IDE卡死，因为 <strong>Android Studio</strong> 配置插件后不会默认导入 <strong>Flutter</strong> 的环境变量。首先进入 <strong>Android Studio</strong> 设置：</p>

<p><img src="/img/flutter/preferences_macox.png" alt="preferences_macox" /></p>

<p>搜索关键字 <strong>flutter</strong>，然后手动指定本地的 <strong>Flutter SDK path</strong>：</p>

<p><img src="/img/flutter/preferences_flutter_macox.png" alt="preferences_flutter_macox" /></p>

<p>设置完毕后重启IDE，在尝试创建工程。如果依然卡死，请在环境变量内配置下载 <strong>Flutter</strong> 的中国依赖源。</p>

<p><img src="/img/flutter/new_flutter_project_page.png" alt="new_flutter_project_page" /></p>
